Ukrainian Banks’ Loss Narrowed in Seven Months to $490 Million

-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 
2011-08-23T12:07:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-23/ukrainian-banks-loss-narrowed-in-seven-months-to-490-million.html
Ukrainian banks’ combined net loss
narrowed in the first seven months of the year, the central bank
said without giving a reason.  The net loss totaled 3.9 billion hryvnia ($490 million),
compared with a loss of 8.6 billion hryvnia for the same period
a year earlier,  Natsionalnyi Bank Ukrainy , which is based in the
capital Kiev, said today in a statement on its  website .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kateryna Choursina in Kiev at 
 kchoursina@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Claudia Carpenter at 
 ccarpenter2@bloomberg.net  